like a hermit.

36:54.003 --> 36:55.546
So this suits me just fine.

36:57.089 --> 36:59.217
If every day is the same here,

36:59.258 --> 37:00.760
that means there'll never
be a full moon.

37:00.801 --> 37:04.096
Sounds like an
upgrade to me.

37:04.138 --> 37:06.098
And besides,

37:06.140 --> 37:08.100
other people and I haven't
gotten on so well

37:08.142 --> 37:09.936
lately, so your father
and I are...

37:09.977 --> 37:12.063
â™ª Of the falling snow... â™ª

37:12.104 --> 37:13.522
All in.

37:17.151 --> 37:18.527
Guess it runs in the family.

37:24.951 --> 37:27.411
Hey. Did you guys know
we're royalty?

37:27.453 --> 37:29.080
(laughs)

37:31.540 --> 37:34.085
(insects chirping)

37:40.758 --> 37:42.301
When did you get back?

37:44.262 --> 37:45.763
Like, an hour
or two ago.

37:47.974 --> 37:50.226
I mean, I figured you'd want
to say goodbye to Raf alone.

37:51.978 --> 37:53.854
You really came through for him.

37:53.896 --> 37:57.066
I promised you I would.

37:57.108 --> 38:00.194
Even if it wasn't
how I figured, but...

38:04.407 --> 38:07.618
You know, the supernova's
still going on.

38:08.995 --> 38:10.788
Lizzie can send you back.

38:10.830 --> 38:12.581
You're not seriously
suggesting

38:12.623 --> 38:14.250
I go back to the prison world.

38:14.292 --> 38:16.085
Maybe.

38:16.127 --> 38:17.878
Maybe for a little while,
maybe until

38:17.920 --> 38:21.173
all of this Necromancer nonsense
blows over.

38:21.215 --> 38:22.675
You'd be with Raf,
you'd be safe.

38:22.717 --> 38:24.260
You wouldn't be there.

38:26.220 --> 38:28.055
I don't see the point.

38:29.557 --> 38:31.767
The point is,
is that I'm scared.

38:31.809 --> 38:36.188
Even though we saved Raf,
it still feels like we lost him,

38:36.230 --> 38:39.150
and you of all people know
what that does to me.

38:39.191 --> 38:41.527
Especially now
that you're human.

38:41.569 --> 38:43.612
You mean weak?
Somebody you're

38:43.654 --> 38:45.364
gonna have to spend the rest
of your life worrying about

38:45.406 --> 38:46.907
and, and-and-and protecting?

38:46.949 --> 38:48.159
Landon...
Now that I'm

38:48.200 --> 38:50.202
not special.
Don't put that on me.

38:50.244 --> 38:52.163
I've never needed you
to be special.

38:52.204 --> 38:53.873
I've always loved you for you.

38:53.914 --> 38:56.334
I love you now.

38:56.375 --> 38:57.668
Why are you picking a fight
about this?

38:57.710 --> 38:59.128
Because not once

38:59.170 --> 39:00.796
today did you say
that it would be okay.

39:00.838 --> 39:02.923
Me giving up everything

39:02.965 --> 39:04.216
that made me fit in
at this school,

39:04.258 --> 39:07.887
everything that makes me fit
with you.

39:07.928 --> 39:09.847
We only work

39:09.889 --> 39:11.640
when I'm unbreakable, and today,
when you were telling me

39:11.682 --> 39:13.100
that I go back to being just me,

39:13.142 --> 39:14.852
you didn't say
that it'd be okay,

39:14.894 --> 39:16.854
that we would be okay.

39:16.896 --> 39:19.065
And I know why you
didn't say it.

39:21.275 --> 39:23.027
'Cause you don't believe it.

39:26.280 --> 39:27.865
Admit that.

39:32.703 --> 39:34.246
(sighs)

39:36.582 --> 39:39.877
I promised Raf that I'd live
my life the best I can.

39:41.670 --> 39:44.465
And what you want
isn't living, Hope.

39:46.634 --> 39:48.135
Not to me.

39:55.851 --> 39:57.436
NECROMANCER:
So, in conclusion,

39:57.478 --> 40:00.648
Malivore is raised,
beholden to me.

40:00.689 --> 40:05.861
All the monsters incarcerated in
his accursed pit are liberated.

40:05.903 --> 40:08.739
And I, the Almighty Necromancer,

40:08.781 --> 40:10.991
shall hold dominion over them

40:11.033 --> 40:14.745
and this entire plane.

40:14.787 --> 40:17.123
(exhales)
(Alyssa clears throat)

40:20.000 --> 40:22.753
shall hold dominion.

40:22.795 --> 40:25.798
Partners.
That's what we said.

40:25.840 --> 40:28.259
(laughs)

40:28.300 --> 40:31.387
It really is none
of your concern.

40:31.429 --> 40:35.975
And not the reason I reunited
your soul with your furry flesh.

40:36.016 --> 40:39.687
Then why am I returned?

40:39.728 --> 40:41.856
Because you're
an all-seeing oracle.

40:41.897 --> 40:43.774
So shouldn't you know?

40:43.816 --> 40:45.443
I surely could.

40:45.484 --> 40:48.237
But I quite like
the way he talks.

40:48.279 --> 40:53.159
Then listen well,
you fantastic man-lion,

40:53.200 --> 40:55.202
and answer me this:

40:55.244 --> 40:58.330
will our plan fail or succeed?

41:08.174 --> 41:11.969
It shall come to pass
as you have described.

41:12.011 --> 41:15.890
Ah! Yeah!

41:15.931 --> 41:18.017
And what about
the Salvatore students?

41:18.058 --> 41:19.727
Will they suffer?

41:19.768 --> 41:21.479
Very much.

41:21.520 --> 41:23.314
And one...

41:23.355 --> 41:24.648
will die.

41:36.869 --> 41:38.913
Told you it'd work.

41:41.707 --> 41:44.543
You were right...

41:44.585 --> 41:46.212
partner.

41:46.253 --> 41:48.255
(laughing)

